LATVIA - BOURSE REOPENING EXTENDED TO THREE HOURS . The Riga stock exchange said on Monday that it was extending the morning reopening trade session to three hours from one starting today . " The morning price fix will now last from 1100 till 1400 ( 0800 - 1000 GMT ) with the central market open for both selling and buying transactions , " the bourse ' s spokeswoman told Reuters . The official statistics for the day ' s trading would be made available around 1600 , she added . - - Riga newsroom , + 371 721 5240 
